{"tid":681002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"AV片商被HACK, 然後我send左個email比個hacker","createTime":"2018-05-27T15:54:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-03T08:58:28.000Z","uid":187050,"like":60,"dislike":864,"uniUserReply":118,"replies":[{"pid":"ec6682845eaab045c4964e152271b1f4f6c65978","tid":681002,"uid":187050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T15:54:00.000Z","msg":"原post傳送門<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/680448/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/680448/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/27/232759_394659692a460258b45a99f1424ea357.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2F232759_394659692a460258b45a99f1424ea357.jpg&h=ad942ce5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n見到個post，大家都淨係問相問link，其實大家有冇諗過最大影響係d女優。Hacker攪Prestige我冇野講，反正呢套流出咪拍下套囉，對間公司根本影響唔大。<br />\n<br />\n但大家有冇諗過對d女優有咩影響？係呀，講緊日日比你打免費J果d女優呀。<br />\n<br />\n第時人地冇咁正，冇咁好J，又或者你地J厭左佢，為左比新鮮感大家，落馬係佢地其中一條最後出路。可以繼續拍多幾套4仔先收皮。<br />\n<br />\n呢刻被落馬，佢地o係AV界o既壽命會短左一大截，其實人地好能慘架。<br />\n<br />\n我send左個email比個hacker，但可能hacker個email已經比yahoo block左send唔到<br />\n<br />\n希望大家如果見到第日果d片流出，或者見到hacker再留email賣片時，可以留個comment或者send個email比hacker，盡男人本份，保護好每晚陪你渡過寂寞的女人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCopy &amp; Paste版如下<br />\n<br />\nHi,<br />\n<br />\nI know you asked Prestige to pay and they refused so you are going to publish those videos. I have no comment about this if it only affects Prestige...<br />\n<br />\nBut please consider the effects on those actresses. Most of them are young, beautiful and popular now. But when they become older or less popular, no big AV company will employ them. At that moment, going to shoot uncensored AV will become one of their way out. By leaking their uncensored video, you guys are shortening their career (or may be life) significantly.<br />\n<br />\nThose actresses provided entertainment for many people around the world, many people even get it free of charge. I think it is our responsibility not to hurt them this way.<br />\n<br />\nThank you very much.<br />\n<br />\nBest Regards,"},{"pid":"4df442ef234e5e32dd931793ad76b260ceffc971","tid":681002,"uid":76115,"like":55,"dislike":3,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T15:55:22.000Z","msg":"哭了"},{"pid":"97d8b69417934d4cb71d37684cd66714270da04f","tid":681002,"uid":11097,"like":472,"dislike":35,"score":437,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T15:56:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/27/235547_332930e7f6894d5f7393b3fe36449949.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2F235547_332930e7f6894d5f7393b3fe36449949.png&h=3eb3ce56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n垃圾你單機啦以後"},{"pid":"e42baced158933b5d1635d1f4a024d23546b3331","tid":681002,"uid":128360,"like":365,"dislike":5,"score":360,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T15:57:35.000Z","msg":"樓豬好撚型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1942210fff0ec2672b1ff78b2a9e19861d11f3b9","tid":681002,"uid":24534,"like":53,"dislike":6,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T15:57:54.000Z","msg":".co.jp <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e30cc4b15a550ee51ee7fc06db1b7a3ce57ad668","tid":681002,"uid":187050,"like":0,"dislike":31,"score":-31,"quote":{"pid":"1942210fff0ec2672b1ff78b2a9e19861d11f3b9","tid":681002,"uid":24534,"like":53,"dislike":6,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T15:57:54.000Z","msg":".co.jp <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T15:59:34.000Z","msg":"冇諗過，試試先"},{"pid":"594c3eb7fe6e00ebcd46db582cf83b14d32f82f1","tid":681002,"uid":152123,"like":340,"dislike":7,"score":333,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27